Nu har vi lanserat en helt ny app som vi hoppas ska kunna f\u00f6renkla vardagen f\u00f6r dig som kund hos oss. Har du n\u00e5gon g\u00e5ng gl\u00f6mt att st\u00e4lla ut ditt sopk\u00e4rl n\u00e4r det \u00e4r dags f\u00f6r soph\u00e4mtning? Eller funderar du p\u00e5 om \u00e5tervinningscentralen har \u00f6ppet? Borgholm Energis nya app \u00e4r fullmatad med fiffiga funktioner \u2013…<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":185,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-contentwithimage.php","meta":{"_expiration-date-status":"","_expiration-date":0,"_expiration-date-type":"","_expiration-date-categories":[],"_expiration-date-options":[],"advanced-sidebar-menu\/link-title":"","advanced-sidebar-menu\/exclude-page":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"
