Den 1 april 2019 blev det lag p\u00e5 att alla ink\u00f6p i offentlig sektor ska faktureras med elektronisk faktura (e-faktura). Det inneb\u00e4r att alla leverant\u00f6rer till offentlig sektor\u00a0 m\u00e5ste skicka e-fakturor enligt en ny standard (PEPPOL BIS BILLING). Borgholm Energi anv\u00e4nder en e-handelstj\u00e4nst i Visma Proceedo med systemleverant\u00f6ren Visma Commerce. Borgholm Energi accepterar inte fakturor…<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":185,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_expiration-date-status":"","_expiration-date":0,"_expiration-date-type":"","_expiration-date-categories":[],"_expiration-date-options":[],"advanced-sidebar-menu\/link-title":"","advanced-sidebar-menu\/exclude-page":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"
